        "markdown_formatted": "## Meeting Purpose\n\n[Train Wiets on Upwork contract management for content writers.](https://fathom.video/share/QnQ4qfE47Cuoh9Dn6WBxL4xtaiexhxye?tab=summary&timestamp=0.0)\n\n## Key Takeaways\n\n  - [Created new milestone for 20 articles at $850 each ($17,000 total) for existing writer](https://fathom.video/share/QnQ4qfE47Cuoh9Dn6WBxL4xtaiexhxye?tab=summary&timestamp=181.0)\n  - [Upwork milestone process: create \u2192 writer accepts \u2192 funds held in escrow \u2192 release payment when work completed](https://fathom.video/share/QnQ4qfE47Cuoh9Dn6WBxL4xtaiexhxye?tab=summary&timestamp=174.0)\n  - [Wiets likely to handle Upwork contracts moving forward; further training planned](https://fathom.video/share/QnQ4qfE47Cuoh9Dn6WBxL4xtaiexhxye?tab=summary&timestamp=383.0)\n\n## Topics\n\n### Upwork Contract Management\n\n  - [Accessed \"Hire Talent\" \u2192 \"Talent I've Hired\" to find existing writer's profile](https://fathom.video/share/QnQ4qfE47Cuoh9Dn6WBxL4xtaiexhxye?tab=summary&timestamp=131.0)\n  - [Current milestone still in progress; Ada will notify when to release payment](https://fathom.video/share/QnQ4qfE47Cuoh9Dn6WBxL4xtaiexhxye?tab=summary&timestamp=170.0)\n  - [Added new milestone: 20 articles, $850 each, totaling $17,000](https://fathom.video/share/QnQ4qfE47Cuoh9Dn6WBxL4xtaiexhxye?tab=summary&timestamp=257.0)\n  - [Milestone creation doesn't require immediate payment; funds sit in escrow](https://fathom.video/share/QnQ4qfE47Cuoh9Dn6WBxL4xtaiexhxye?tab=summary&timestamp=181.0)\n  - [\"Active and Funded\" status indicates milestone is set up and awaiting work completion](https://fathom.video/share/QnQ4qfE47Cuoh9Dn6WBxL4xtaiexhxye?tab=summary&timestamp=337.0)\n\n### Upwork Interface Navigation\n\n  - [Milestone creation usually prompts funding page (didn't occur this time)](https://fathom.video/share/QnQ4qfE47Cuoh9Dn6WBxL4xtaiexhxye?tab=summary&timestamp=300.0)\n  - [System sends contract to writer for acceptance](https://fathom.video/share/QnQ4qfE47Cuoh9Dn6WBxL4xtaiexhxye?tab=summary&timestamp=305.0)\n  - [Once accepted, typically prompts to select funding account for escrow](https://fathom.video/share/QnQ4qfE47Cuoh9Dn6WBxL4xtaiexhxye?tab=summary&timestamp=305.0)\n\n### Team Roles and Training\n\n  - [Uncertainty about who will manage Upwork contracts long-term](https://fathom.video/share/QnQ4qfE47Cuoh9Dn6WBxL4xtaiexhxye?tab=summary&timestamp=383.0)\n  - [Wiets likely candidate for handling contracts due to current team size](https://fathom.video/share/QnQ4qfE47Cuoh9Dn6WBxL4xtaiexhxye?tab=summary&timestamp=402.0)\n  - [Molly to discuss with Bridget about role distribution and further training needs](https://fathom.video/share/QnQ4qfE47Cuoh9Dn6WBxL4xtaiexhxye?tab=summary&timestamp=408.0)\n\n## Next Steps\n\n  - [Molly to consult with Bridget about task allocation and Wiets' training needs](https://fathom.video/share/QnQ4qfE47Cuoh9Dn6WBxL4xtaiexhxye?tab=summary&timestamp=408.0)\n  - [Wiets to potentially take over Upwork contract management](https://fathom.video/share/QnQ4qfE47Cuoh9Dn6WBxL4xtaiexhxye?tab=summary&timestamp=408.0)\n  - [Monitor current writer's progress for payment release (Ada to notify)](https://fathom.video/share/QnQ4qfE47Cuoh9Dn6WBxL4xtaiexhxye?tab=summary&timestamp=174.0)\n  - [Await writer's acceptance of new milestone for 20 articles](https://fathom.video/share/QnQ4qfE47Cuoh9Dn6WBxL4xtaiexhxye?tab=summary&timestamp=257.0)\n"
